## Description

Pytorch code for TM-GCN method, a Dynamic Graph Convolutional Networks Using the Tensor M-Product. PNAS paper (https://www.pnas.org/content/118/28/e2015851118.short), SIAM paper (https://epubs.siam.org/doi/abs/10.1137/1.9781611976700.82), IBM blog (https://research.ibm.com/blog/new-tensor-algebra)
